{
  "stem": "24346.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They guarded the rail track where we arrived from both sides and from all over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us walking into the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So these people-- once we came to the camp, they handed us over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They counted-- you know, it accounts for-- These guys left and the guards from the camp took over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, we had to disrobe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, this is a new chapter in itself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us to a bath.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, we had to disrobe to the bird suit-- naked, completely naked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Had to drop everything, leave it in a pile-- the suit-- went into a bath.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Went, I remember, it was a big tub, a very big tub-- 50, 60 people could go in one shot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was filled with chemicals, and there was anti-lice, to kill lice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And before we went in there, a barber cut, shaved-- not shaved, but he took off, with a machine, all the hair, from all over-- under arms, armpits, all over, wherever a person has hair, they cleaned it off.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And where we went into that [NON-ENGLISH], they used to call it, to kill the lice, that was burning, that chemical was burning like hell.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Obviously, it went with the machine too close under the armpits and ripped some skin off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Didn't feel it before, but you went in-- and my God, [INAUDIBLE], burning like hell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But maybe this was a must because they tried to eliminate lice, because the sanitary conditions were bad-- no hot water, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, we were assigned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us to barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the barracks were--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Went out the other side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, in fact, it was January of 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
